T. reichi
) aestethascs. Antenna peduncle articles 1–3 short, subequal, articles 4–5 long and slender; flagellum longer than peduncle, with 11–17 (most species) or 25–27 articles (
T. lepturoides
,
sp. nov .
); antenna length about 0,3x (most species) up to 0,5x BL (
